title: 08/16/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 08/16/21 DPS Best Of
description:
Doug Gottlieb and Rob Parker, in for Dan, discuss the first impressions of rookie quarterbacks during their preseason debuts. The guys debate Tom Brady's accolades. Doug and Rob react to the new-look Lakers and discuss where they belong in the current landscape of the Western Conference. Matt Hayes of 1010 XL Jacksonville joins the guys to react to Tim Tebow's Jaguars debut and explain why there is major optimism for the Urban Meyer regime in Jacksonville.
